The make.clr command converts a [[Shared_file | shared]] file to a [[Clr_file | centered log ratio]] file. The make.clr command parameters are shared, groups, zero and label. The shared file is required.

==Default Settings==
The shared file is required.

 mothur > make.clr(shared=final.opti_mcc.shared)

